item.title: JrGRAS2
item.description: Gene Details: Gene ID: Gene Symbol: JrGRAS2 Gene Name: GRAS TF 2 Genome: Species: Juglans regia Functional Descriptions: JrGRAS2 improves plant HT tolerance involving in HSP expression.

item.title: JrLAC12–1
item.description: Gene Details: Gene ID: Gene Symbol: JrLAC12–1 Gene Name: laccase-12-like Genome: Species: Juglans regia Functional Descriptions: JrLAC12–1, JrLAC12–2 and JrLAC16 showed a significant change in expression at the lignification stage.

item.title: JrPPO1
item.description: Gene Details: Gene ID: Gene Symbol: JrPPO1 Gene Name: Genome: Species: Juglans regia Functional Descriptions: JrPPO1 was highly expressed in stems, young leaves, mature leaves, catkins, pistils, and hulls.

item.title: JrPPO2
item.description: Gene Details: Gene ID: Gene Symbol: JrPPO2 Gene Name: Genome: Species: Juglans regia Functional Descriptions: JrPPO2 was highly expressed in mature leaves and pistils.
